caption:
Launching into grocery stores as a small business means that we had to learn *a lot* of new terminology — so we’re spilling the tea behind what the heck even is “merchandising” 🤔

PS. You can now find us in every @sprouts in the nation — we’re part of a 90-day trial to determine if we stick around permanently on their shelves! So find a store near you, look for the “New For You” sign, + grab your fave Saucy Noodles today ✨
